extendedInfo.description: Help keep your vehicle on the road and out of the repair shop with the Jiffy LubeÂ® App. Find the nearest Jiffy Lube. Get tips. Store important vehicle information. Itâs all at the tip of your fingers with the Jiffy Lube App.Features:Locator: Find Jiffy Lube locations quickly with the locator feature. You can get directions, call the location directly, and find out what services are offered at that location. You can also download the $5 off coupon for the Jiffy Lube Signature ServiceÂ® Oil Change.MyInfo: Conveniently store photos of important vehicle documents such as registration, insurance cards and license plates for handy access*. Car tips are also provided to provide quick, helpful information in the event of an emergency, such as how to jump-start your battery.MyGarage: Schedule reminders for important routine maintenance checks, such as tire pressure, coolant level and wiper blades. Each item on the list also comes with âhow-toâ instructions.Jiffy Lube: Allows you to connect to Jiffy Lube in more ways. Here you can find general information on warranties, a list of services offered, general information on oil and a link to the Jiffy Lube Facebook page.

reviews.title: Worth the trouble
reviews.comment: This app crashes way more often than it should. However, it works well enough and long enough to get to coupon page. Thus despite having to deal with a few crashes, it paid off immediately.

reviews.title: Won\'t quit or exit.
reviews.comment: That\'s why I uninstalled it!  Hitting the \"back\" button on my phone is supposed to close the app (unless there\'s a specific \"quit\" or \"exit\"  button.  And this has nothing to do with the app staying resident in the background.  Your app should at least behave like 99% of the other apps, or nobody is going to want to use it!
